Wed May 27 05:49:42 UTC 2026 - Martin Hauke <mardnh@gmx.de>

- Update to version 0.1.4
  Added
  * SourceCode paragraph style renders as a distinct code block in
    all export formats and the TUI.
  * Text inside wps:txbx shape text boxes is now extracted and
    rendered with box-drawing borders instead of being silently
    dropped.
  Fixed
  * Numbered list items sharing the same abstract numbering
    definition now count sequentially instead of both restarting
    at 1.
  * Bullet-format list levels (numFmt="bullet") no longer render
    as lettered sequences.
  * w:br line break elements inside a run are now preserved,
    fixing multi-line code blocks concatenated into a single line.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Tue Oct 21 17:23:33 UTC 2025 - Martin Hauke <mardnh@gmx.de>

- Update to version 0.1.2
  Added
  * Inline Equation Support.
  * ANSI Export Format.
  * Strikethrough Support.
  Fixed
  * Integration Tests for Packaging.
  * Text Formatting Preservation.
  * Word Automatic List Formatting.
  * File Type Validation.
  * Equation Positioning (Partial Fix).
  Misc
  * Dependency Upgrades
  * Help text updated to document new search state toggle
    functionality.
  * Improved error messages for invalid file formats with specific
    guidance.
  * Enhanced equation extraction to track paragraph positions for
    better document structure.

